                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10045" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1505</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">573 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百亿业绩补偿迷局：天山股份并购承诺的博弈与揭晓</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Billion-Dollar Performance Compensation Puzzle: The Game and Revelation of the Merger Promise of Tianshan Cement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李金茹，翁铭璐，王欣然，刘家鑫，全娜，王研，张玥瑶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天山材料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业绩承诺；业绩补偿；减值补偿；天山股份；中国建材</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Performance commitment; performance compensation; impairment compensation; Tianshan Cement; China National Building Materials</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦天山股份并购后，因被并购方业绩承诺未达标，产生百亿补偿又巧妙化解事件。天山股份在水泥行业困境下毅然决定开启并购征程，达成A股史上第三大并购案，交易完成后，天山股份乘势而成水泥行业龙头。并购过程中，因市场寒潮致需求骤降、煤价暴涨成本上升、行业产能过剩等因素，天山股份虽有庞大产能但业绩却颓势尽显，受多方因素影响大幅下滑，最终中国建材的业绩承诺完成率竟不足四成，触发百亿补偿。而补偿方案暗含妙处，涉及现金补偿、股份补偿，以及回购注销股份等操作，化解了超百亿的补偿僵局，提供了“现金+股权”的突破困境的范本方案。本案例旨在探究其补偿协议究竟有何合理性、合规性和巧妙之处，以供行业借鉴，同时引导与帮助学生借助此案例学习业绩承诺和补偿协议方面的规定与技巧。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on the ingenious resolution of a compensation of over 10 billion yuan ,due to the failure of the acquired party to meet its performance commitment after the merger of Tianshan Cement. Despite the difficult situation in the cement industry, Tianshan Cement resolutely embarked on a merger journey and completed the third-largest merger in A-share history. After the transaction, Tianshan Cement became the leader in the cement industry. During the merger process, due to factors such as a sudden drop in demand caused by a market cold spell, a sharp increase in coal prices leading to rising costs, and overcapacity in the industry, Tianshan Cement, despite having a large production capacity, showed a significant decline in performance. Affected by multiple factors, its performance dropped sharply, and the completion rate of China National Building Materials&#39; performance commitment was less than 40%, triggering a compensation of over 10 billion yuan. The compensation plan contained ingenious elements, involving cash compensation, share compensation, and the repurchase and cancellation of shares, resolving the compensation deadlock of over 10 billion yuan and providing a model solution of &quot;cash + equity&quot; to break through the predicament. The rationality, compliance, and ingenuity of the compensation agreement are worth in-depth exploration for industry reference.  Meanwhile, it guides and helps students learn the regulations and skills related to performance commitments and compensation agreements through this case.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《企业并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业并购动因；业绩承诺；业绩补偿方式；减值补偿</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
